Your plans abroad are not exactly minimalist, so far you have acted in Madrid, Brussels, London or Moscow.
The Tap Tap is a group of people with disabilities.
What is the logistics and organization of these trips?
It’s not as difficult as it may seem at first glance.
There are five members in electric wheelchairs, the chairs must travel in the luggage compartment and also we carry a lot of weight, the boxes with the instruments...
