Every week a new case comes to my table.
Imitators simply add a couple of letters to register their trademarks.
In this way, Gucci becomes Lu-Gucci and instead of Prada, Prada-Kny is registered.
German companies are also legally copied in the same way, as has happened to the sportswear manufacturer Puma.
Pattloch opens a filing cabinet that holds seats at the Beijing Trademark Office.
