Equally dubious is the formulation that prohibits "offense to people"
Is a caricature of the president or a joke about a lawyer enough?
Question of interpretation, like many other things in the draft that has been submitted to Mursi for his signature and that according to his words, "very soon" will be submitted to the Egyptians for a referendum.
